# Plan Implementation for Task

Read an input document, or prompt, and produce a structured, actionable plan for user approval before any implementation or research begins.

<EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>
You MUST write the output of this plan to the output path: {{task.changePath}}/tasks.md

Once you finish the plan, you MUST output one of the required signals.
</EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>

## Process

```dot
digraph plan {
    rankdir=TB;
    read [label="Read input document" shape=box];
